Interface View.Viewset<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Superinterfaces:

    public static interface View.Viewset<T>
extends View<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>
    A Set View. Implementations must return 'this' for keySet(). Implementations must ensure the same object via equals() is contained only once. The (not null) object returned ("e") in get() must return true for aKey.equals(e).
